SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM :1 A LEFT OUTER JOIN :2 D ON (D.BE_SYMBOOL = A.TR_SYMBOOL AND D.BE_OPTIETYPE = A.TR_OPTIETYPE AND D.BE_EXPIRATIEDATUM = A.TR_EXPIRATIEDATUM AND D.BE_EXERCISEPRIJS = A.TR_EXERCISEPRIJS) LEFT OUTER JOIN :3 E ON (E.TS_SYMBOOL = A.TR_INDICATIE) WHERE A.TR_TRANSNUMMER BETWEEN ~4 AND ~5 AND A.TR_MUT_GEMAAKT <> 'N' AND A.TR_INDICATIE NOT IN ('T-G', 'S-G', 'TV V', 'TV K', 'TV A', 'YTD', 'TOEK', 'LOSB', 'EXP') AND (A.TR_INDICATIE NOT IN ('D', 'L', 'O', 'OMWL', 'OMWS') OR A.TR_NOTABEDRAG <> 0) AND (A.TR_INDICATIE not in ('BLEV','BONT') OR A.TR_PRIJS_TR_MNTSRT <> 0 AND ~6 <> 1) AND NOT ((A.TR_INDICATIE = 'K' OR A.TR_INDICATIE = 'V') AND D.BE_BI_NUMMER BETWEEN 600 AND 699 AND A.TR_NOTABEDRAG = 0) AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM :8 F WHERE A.TR_VOLGNUMMER = F.GBM_TR_ID) :7
